    "### ComparaciÃ³n por distancia\n",
    "\n",
    "Se dous audios teÃ±en pegadas parecidas, a distancia serÃ¡ pequena.\n",
    "Usaremos distancia euclÃ­dea (sinxela)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def dist(a, b):\n",
    "    return float(np.linalg.norm(a - b))\n",
    "\n",
    "distancia = dist(fp1, fp2)\n",
    "print(\"Distancia fp1â€“fp2:\", round(distancia, 4))"
   ]
