    "## 5) Mini-clasificador por regras (sen IA)\n",
    "\n",
    "Exemplo de regra:\n",
    "- Se o centroide medio Ã© alto â†’ mÃ¡is brillante\n",
    "- Se o ZCR medio Ã© alto â†’ mÃ¡is ruÃ­doso\n",
    "\n",
    "Imos facer unha funciÃ³n que "describe" un audio."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def describir(fp):\n",
    "    rms_m, rms_s, cent_m, cent_s, zcr_m, zcr_s = fp\n",
    "    desc = []\n",
    "    desc.append(\"mÃ¡is forte\" if rms_m > 0.05 else \"mÃ¡is suave\")\n",
    "    desc.append(\"mÃ¡is brillante\" if cent_m > 2000 else \"mÃ¡is escuro\")\n",
    "    desc.append(\"mÃ¡is ruÃ­doso\" if zcr_m > 0.08 else \"mÃ¡is limpo\")\n",
    "    return \", \".join(desc)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Audio1:\", describir(fp1))\n",
    "print(\"Audio2:\", describir(fp2))"
   ]
